name: iEmu
tagline: Adding support s5l89xx support to QEMU, and then running it on your computer.
body:
#iEmu
### Mission
To get the iOS booting in QEMU on different hardware platforms (iPhone, iPod, iPad, (Apple Watch?), etc)
### Git (Source)
The fork we are currently working on is available [here](https://www.github.com/awesomebing1/iEmu/).
### Help us
Create issues! Create pull requests! If you really need to email me, do it by clicking my email button here: @awesomebing1
### Current Status
Really buggy. Currently, there is only support for the first iPhone (iPhone 2G).
